arStrings.szText: You killed them! I don’t know if they were tracking you or me. Caldeum has always been a cesspit, but it was livable until the Knights took the city. Now everyone is gone. Jazem too...
Surprised that the knights were killed so easily by the Player. Hader is mournful when he mentions Jazem.
I haven’t time to mourn now. I need to leave. I wouldn’t stick around either. Akarat guide you.
Shakes off emotion from previous line
